<plot>The premise of this film is a response to the overall ignorance of some people when it comes to pre-judging certain racial groups. The story centers around a high school racist white girl and the unfortunate events that happen to her as a result of her ignorance and racist ideas. Our actions have consequences -- bad things often happen when people are confronted with human imperfection and perhaps a little revenge.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?417618</url></doc>
